# =========================
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.vite/
**/.cache/
**/coverage/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# myPokemon_AJ: tsconfig에 outDir가 없어 tsc가 src 옆에 만든 산출물
myPokemon_AJ/src/**/*.js
myPokemon_AJ/src/**/*.js.map

# =========================
